column2: In addition to Facebook, what would be the best way(s) for you to connect with the rest of the Aspirations community?
A specific website or page with a way to connect
I'm not sure what the Facebook has, but I find that email is a really good way to connect and so I hope to get some emails within the community.
Amazing resources for connection would include Snapchat and Instagram.

A forum with filtered topics so it is easy and clear to find new opportunities for differing ages like college or high school, internships, job opportunities
